    <item>
      <title>石油市场正处于风险升级的环境中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/oil-market-is-in-an-escalatory-risk-environment-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 OPEC+ 会议之前，Rapidan Energy 创始人鲍勃·麦克纳利 (Bob McNally) 认为，由于地缘政治紧张局势带来的“风险升级”，油价上涨 40 美元的可能性为 30%，本周伊朗声称以色列杀害了其在叙利亚的指挥官。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-03/oil-market-is-in-an-escalatory-risk-environment-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:26:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco加大了对美联储降息幅度将低于全球同行的债券押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/pimco-boosts-bond-bets-that-fed-will-cut-less-than-global-peers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司的安德鲁·鲍尔斯表示，债券市场押注美联储在未来几年降息幅度将低于其他主要央行的时机已经成熟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/pimco-boosts-bond-bets-that-fed-will-cut-less-than-global-peers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港放宽改变身份证性别的手术要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/hong-kong-eases-surgery-requirement-for-changing-sex-on-id-cards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港放宽了对跨性别者的一些规定，以便改变官方身份证上的性别，但仍保留强制进行某些类型手术的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/hong-kong-eases-surgery-requirement-for-changing-sex-on-id-cards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 09:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
