      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/china-s-tussle-with-yuan-bears-risks-triggering-sharp-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对人民币的捍卫正走向一个里程碑时刻，可能会引发当局采取更强有力的反应来惩罚卖空者。]]></description>
